{"tha-ap53:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap53:0.2":"Bijanivagga ","tha-ap53:0.3":"Vidhupanadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap53:1.1":"“Padumuttarabuddhassa, ","tha-ap53:1.2":"lokajetthassa tadino; ","tha-ap53:1.3":"Bijanika maya dinna, ","tha-ap53:1.4":"dvipadindassa tadino. ","tha-ap53:2.1":"Sakam cittam pasadetva, ","tha-ap53:2.2":"paggahetvana anjalim; ","tha-ap53:2.3":"Sambuddhamabhivadetva, ","tha-ap53:2.4":"pakkamim uttaramukho. ","tha-ap53:3.1":"Bijanim paggahetvana, ","tha-ap53:3.2":"sattha lokagganayako; ","tha-ap53:3.3":"Bhikkhusanghe thito santo, ","tha-ap53:3.4":"ima gatha abhasatha. ","tha-ap53:4.1":"‘Imina bijanidanena, ","tha-ap53:4.2":"cittassa panidhihi ca; ","tha-ap53:4.3":"Kappanam satasahassam, ","tha-ap53:4.4":"vinipatam na gacchati’. ","tha-ap53:5.1":"Araddhaviriyo pahitatto, ","tha-ap53:5.2":"Cetogunasamahito; ","tha-ap53:5.3":"Jatiya sattavassoham, ","tha-ap53:5.4":"Arahattam apapunim. ","tha-ap53:6.1":"Satthikappasahassamhi, ","tha-ap53:6.2":"bijamanasanamaka; ","tha-ap53:6.3":"Solasasimsu rajano, ","tha-ap53:6.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap53:7.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap53:7.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap53:7.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap53:7.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap53:8.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma vidhupanadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap53:9.1":"Vidhupanadayakattherassapadanam pathamam. "}